TITLE: Configuring Prometheus Exporter and Scraper in Alloy
DESCRIPTION: Sets up a local system metrics exporter and configures a scraper to collect metrics every 10 seconds. The scraper will forward the collected metrics to a filtering component.
SOURCE: https://github.com/grafana/alloy/blob/main/docs/sources/tutorials/send-metrics-to-prometheus.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: alloy
CODE:
```
