TITLE: Complete Alloy Configuration with Kuma Discovery and Prometheus Integration
DESCRIPTION: A comprehensive example showing how to configure Kuma service discovery, Prometheus scraping, and remote write in Grafana Alloy. It demonstrates the integration between discovery.kuma, prometheus.scrape, and prometheus.remote_write components.
SOURCE: https://github.com/grafana/alloy/blob/main/docs/sources/reference/components/discovery/discovery.kuma.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: alloy
CODE:
```
discovery.kuma "example" {
    server     = "http://kuma-control-plane.kuma-system.svc:5676"
}
prometheus.scrape "demo" {
    targets    = discovery.kuma.example.targets
    forward_to = [prometheus.remote_write.demo.receiver]
}
prometheus.remote_write "demo" {
    endpoint {
        url = "<PROMETHEUS_REMOTE_WRITE_URL>"
        basic_auth {
            username = "<USERNAME>"
            password = "<PASSWORD>"
        }
    }
}
```

