SOURCE: https://github.com/grafana/alloy/blob/main/docs/sources/set-up/migrate/from-prometheus.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
global:
  scrape_timeout:    45s

scrape_configs:
  - job_name: "prometheus"
    static_configs:
      - targets: ["localhost:12345"]

remote_write:
  - name: "grafana-cloud"
    url: "https://prometheus-us-central1.grafana.net/api/prom/push"
    basic_auth:
      username: <USERNAME>
      password: <PASSWORD>
```

