TITLE: Configuring CloudWatch Exporter for SQS Metrics in Alloy
DESCRIPTION: This Alloy configuration snippet sets up a CloudWatch exporter job for AWS SQS queues. It defines the AWS region, discovery type, and specific metrics to collect such as NumberOfMessagesSent and NumberOfMessagesReceived.
SOURCE: https://github.com/grafana/alloy/blob/main/docs/sources/reference/components/prometheus/prometheus.exporter.cloudwatch.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: alloy
CODE:
```
