TITLE: Configuring Grafana Alloy as Linux Systemd Service
DESCRIPTION: This systemd service file defines how to run Grafana Alloy as a service. It includes service dependencies, restart behavior, and execution parameters. Replace <WORKING_DIRECTORY> and <BINARY_PATH> with appropriate values.
