TITLE: Relabeling Metrics with prometheus.relabel in Alloy
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to use the prometheus.relabel component to add an 'os' label to metrics scraped from a unix exporter. It uses the constants.os value to set the label and forwards the relabeled metrics to a Prometheus remote write endpoint.
